JEST
----
Jest is a powerful and easy-to-use testing framework for JavaScript applications. 
It works well with popular libraries like React, Angular, Node.js, and Vanilla JavaScript.


Test syntax
------------
test(description, callback) or it(description, callback)



Matchers
--------
Jest provides matchers to compare values:

    -toBe: For strict equality (===).
    -toEqual: For deep equality (objects, arrays).

